Designing challenge questions for location‐based authentication systems: a real‐life study
</dc:title>
<dc:creator>Albayram Y.</dc:creator>
<prism:publicationName>Human-centric Computing and Information Sciences</prism:publicationName>
<prism:eIssn>21921962</prism:eIssn>
<prism:volume>5</prism:volume>
