Performance of Landsat 8 Operational Land Imager for mapping ice sheet velocity
</dc:title>
<dc:creator>Jeong S.</dc:creator>
<prism:publicationName>Remote Sensing of Environment</prism:publicationName>
<prism:issn>00344257</prism:issn>
