Breeding failure induces large scale prospecting movements in the black-legged kittiwake
</dc:title>
<dc:creator>Ponchon A.</dc:creator>
<prism:publicationName>Journal of Experimental Marine Biology and Ecology</prism:publicationName>
<prism:issn>00220981</prism:issn>
<prism:volume>473</prism:volume>
