Basis Construction for Range Estimation by Phase Unwrapping
</dc:title>
<dc:creator>Akhlaq A.</dc:creator>
<prism:publicationName>IEEE Signal Processing Letters</prism:publicationName>
<prism:issn>10709908</prism:issn>
<prism:volume>22</prism:volume>
