A prototype hail detection algorithm and hail climatology developed with the advanced microwave sounding unit (AMSU)
</dc:title>
<dc:creator>Ferraro R.</dc:creator>
<prism:publicationName>Atmospheric Research</prism:publicationName>
<prism:issn>01698095</prism:issn>
