Towards Cost-Efficient Video Transcoding in Media Cloud: Insights Learned from User Viewing Patterns
</dc:title>
<dc:creator>Gao G.</dc:creator>
<prism:publicationName>IEEE Transactions on Multimedia</prism:publicationName>
<prism:issn>15209210</prism:issn>
