Using Lunar Observations to Validate Clouds and the Earth's Radiant Energy System Pointing Accuracy
</dc:title>
<dc:creator>Daniels J.</dc:creator>
<prism:publicationName>IEEE Transactions on Geoscience and Remote Sensing</prism:publicationName>
