Cooperative joint synchronization and localization in wireless sensor networks
</dc:title>
<dc:creator>Vaghefi R.</dc:creator>
<prism:publicationName>IEEE Transactions on Signal Processing</prism:publicationName>
<prism:issn>1053587X</prism:issn>
<prism:volume>63</prism:volume>
