Mobile Node Localization via Pareto Optimization: Algorithm and Fundamental Performance Limitations
</dc:title>
<dc:creator>De Angelis A.</dc:creator>
<prism:publicationName>IEEE Journal on Selected Areas in Communications</prism:publicationName>
<prism:issn>07338716</prism:issn>
<prism:volume>33</prism:volume>
